      "description": "The Corgi U.S. Equities 10% Structured Buffer ETF - June Series (JUNC) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in downside hedge alternatives. The fund is an actively managed ETF, using FLEX options to provide the price return of SPDR S&P 500 ETF Trust to a cap while providing a buffer against the first 10% decline on an annual basis. This series begins on June 1 of each year. JUNC was launched on Jun 1, 2026 and is issued by Corgi.",
